Summary: Leading edge black line effect over Dubuque, Iowa.
divs: Sighting DetailsI was traveling North on US 151 in Downtown Dubuque, IA when noticed a leading edge black line event moving west at a high rate of speed. Prior to that I was seeing a near total white-out south of town from aeresol spraying which looked like it was from four different contrails or sources. The previous night I was in Maquoketa and was seeing extremely heavy metalic particles suspended in air and vibrating with an amber or iodine looking tint right after sunset. They had been falling from the sky the entire afternoon.
